headline: West Pharmaceutical Services’s (NYSE:WST) Q4 CY2025: Beats On Revenue, Stock Soars
summary: Healthcare products company West Pharmaceutical Services (NYSE:WST) reported Q4 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 7.5% year on year to $805 million. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $3.25 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.04 per share was 11.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
